VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT http\.Request|http\.RequestForm|http\.FormValue
WHEN EXPR MISSING:Validate|validate|sanitize|regexp\.MustCompile|strconv\.Atoi|strconv\.ParseInt|json\.Unmarshal
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of HTTP request parameters without proper validation and sanitization.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Inputs: HTTP Request Parameters.
